profile:
Kawartha Window Cleaning offers a personalized window cleaning service that you won't get with a corporation or franchise.  Locally owned and operated, we take pride in our work and hold customer retention through great service and quality of work. 
Kawartha Window cleaning offers: 
- interior/exterior window cleaning of all types of windows
- residential/commercial contracts
- siding wash
- gutter cleaning
